      "description": "Feedforward neural network (3 hidden layers, 128 units each, ReLU activations) trained on 1200 CFD-derived hemolysis samples. Training run with seed A (seed=42). Holdout RMSE: 0.0031 normalised hemolysis index units. R²: 0.983. Maximum absolute error across 5 operating-point clusters: 4.2 %. Model correctly ranked all 5 flow-speed combinations by hemolysis severity. Performance judged to meet the MRL 2 acceptance threshold of RMSE < 0.005.",
