      "rationale": "All 1500 training and holdout samples are generated from CFD simulations of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump at flow rates 2–6 L/min and rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM, matching the CPB COU envelope. Blood rheology and boundary conditions are consistent with the COU specification."
    },
