      "rationale": "Inference is performed in 64-bit floating point. Deterministic output confirmed by re-running inference on 50 holdout samples with fixed weights; bit-identical results obtained across 10 repeated evaluations. Solver error is negligible relative to the 5 % acceptance threshold."
