      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input normalisation pipeline is automated and validated; out-of-range inputs trigger documented warnings.",
      "rationale": "Input features are normalised via a fixed scaler fitted on training data and stored alongside model weights. Out-of-range inputs (beyond training envelope) trigger a logged warning and are flagged in the output record. User guide documents the normalisation procedure and range checks."
