      "acceptanceCriteria": "Holdout sample size is sufficient for reliable RMSE estimation at the required precision.",
      "rationale": "The 300-sample holdout set provides a 95 % confidence interval on RMSE of approximately ±0.0003 units based on bootstrap resampling, which is adequate for the MRL 2 decision. Sample size was determined by a power analysis targeting detection of a 10 % degradation in RMSE with 80 % power."
