    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The neural network surrogate achieves holdout RMSE of 0.0031 (seed A) and 0.0034 (seed B), both below the 0.005 threshold, and correctly ranks all five operating points by hemolysis severity. The two-seed comparison was judged to demonstrate adequate repeatability. The six remaining factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. The package is accepted for use in the CPB COU.",
